    "concept_sort_game": "The aktibo concept ayusin laro interface for categorization magsanay. I-drag aytem into the correct kategorya buckets to demonstrate understanding of classification concepts. Immediate feedback ipinapakita correct and incorrect placements. suporta 2-4 mga kategorya and any numero of sortable aytem. Great for bokabularyo tiers, science classifications, or grammar sorting.",
